Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.71,0:00:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, look...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.16,0:00:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.67,0:00:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's okay if I say something\Nreally amazing right now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I say "No," you're going to anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.99,0:00:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel a sharp increase in flabbiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.81,0:00:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A sharp increase! The flesh has expanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.92,0:00:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see much difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Robo. You think so too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.47,0:00:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You sense a significant weight gain as well, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.85,0:00:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Those legs are elephantine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's like there's a pair of cow's teats up front!\NWe're on the cusp of a new species of animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just too frightening!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.44,0:00:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to get that worked up about, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:00:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just overthinking things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are eating to make you so fat, Wota?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.94,0:01:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about ME?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tired of this, so can we stop\NDERAILING the conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.27,0:01:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, Robo said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.61,0:01:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mic check
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,JK
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.27,0:01:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Soko wa futsuu one-two ga best?
