Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:47.93,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Second-year Class Assignments\N{\an8}(If you wish to change courses, please notify staff ASAP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:47.93,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Robo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Kanade Ninomae, have done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she might go the Science route...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I thought she might go with Liberal Arts\Nto stay with Tanaka-san and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Liberal\N{\an7}Arts\N{\an8}Shiori Saginomiya\N{\an8}Akane Kikuchi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I gambled on, and I hit the jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a dream, Saginomiya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,To think, we'd be in the same class again\Nfor our second year!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Dude, didn't turn in your request form?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Pending\N{\an8}Nozomu Tanaka
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I turned it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Request Form, 2nd-year Course Selection\N{\an7}Please circle your preferred course\N{\an7}Liberal Arts\N{\an7}Science\N{\an7}Other (Enter "Undecided," etc.)\N{\an7}"Dozing Off Course"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask just to make sure:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what "career path" actually means?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, I can't be pigeonholed into some "group."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's like being, you know, holier than fowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you mean, holier than thou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you got that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you've only ever gotten\Nsingle digits on your math tests, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just circle Liberal Arts and turn your sheet in already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I did get a double-digit score\Nthe other day. It was a 10!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to act proud over getting a 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you just sullied the 10 points\NI almost killed myself to earn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure, you're so amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Even rotting your brains out with that "boy's love" stuff,\Nyou're still able to score a whopping 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,BL has nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure get defensive when you\Nhear the word "BL," huh? Lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell, man?! Now you've pissed me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't talk to me for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! Who'd wanna talk to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. This happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But wouldn't it be better if someone intervened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how this works.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a little trick to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she harping on me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she in heat or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now. Just calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just 'cause she can do a little bit better than me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like she looks down on me\Nand treats me like an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll be passing down handouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that?\NWasn't that just totally inappropriate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Why don't you sharpen this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, that fool is rotten to the core!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Her proclivities are rotten too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, that was a good burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This pencil shaving...\Nit's like one long, unbroken string!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Robo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see that fool's face while I'm eating,\Nso I'm going to the cafeteria!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, do you mind if I join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell is her problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind threading this needle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Suits me fine, not having to look at that ugly mug!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Color me happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! It totally won't go through!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit, dammit, dammi-!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you've finished lunch,\Nwould you mind balancing this evenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And once it becomes balanced,\Nyou can have that drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I'm not even that angry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not like I can back down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wota!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it to balance evenly! That's awesome, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot. Give me the tweezers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The right side is a bit heavier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There. Now it's balanced evenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this sight that I'm being shown?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That was awesome, Wota!\NHey, by any chance, are you a Libra?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my. That was faster than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nah, I'm a Pisces. And today's horoscope\Nsaid my lucky item is lactobacillus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had already readied my next stratagem...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Lactobacillus?! So that's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, that "trick" you mentioned earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Not lactobacillus bifidus, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When overwriting undesired information,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:45.88,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Anger
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,it is effective to introduce a new task\Nthat produces feelings of pleasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:46.63,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Bubble Wrap\N{\an7}Anger
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:47.38,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Bubble Wrap\N{\an7}Anger\N{\an8}Pencil Shaving
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:48.13,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Needle Threading\N{\an8}Bubble Wrap\N{\an7}Anger\N{\an8}Pencil Shaving
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,particularly for someone with\Na limited brain capacity like Baka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like you're really\Nmaking fun of Tanaka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You are shortsighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She is... a legitimate idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Note: Using the same word as her nickname, "Majime"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,L-legitimate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. You drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. You drink it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. You drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't hear of it. You drink it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Robo, what is that? A game?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Othello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have the black pieces. Put one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, vertically, horizontally, diagonally...\NYou can turn them all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! That looks like it'd be a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That felt wicked good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do all white next!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She was indeed "legitimate."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll line them up, so you go next, Wota!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, like, when I was in elementary school...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to try bringing dried sardines back to life,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,so I put them in a fish tank overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Robo-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}so I put them in a fish tank overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't know her real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You are just unrepentantly stupid, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All I know is, that's what her friends call her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It must suck to be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wota, you've never tried that before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Her friend, "Baka-san," simply talks a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I do something so idiotic?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:08:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}All things considered,\Nshe's like a pastry with nothing inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:08:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the next day, I checked the fish tank all excited,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but they were still all dried up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Wota-san" is bright-eyed\Nand always has a witty comeback...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing I got out of it was some good fish stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they were sardines, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She's like some bird of prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't doubt you got some good stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Still, it was such a shock at the time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume they gave each other their nicknames,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}but those are some rather bold\Nand straightforward names.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that it felt like I was in a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what would be more shocking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting dried sardines in a tank\Nand they do come back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Robo-san is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She's as lovely as the bright blue Nemophila!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if when she boards this train,\Nit becomes a field of Nemophila, a wave of azure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, whatcha eat last night?\NWe had yaki udon at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, we had katsu don over at ours, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice! A big, fat katsu don!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out with the "big" and "fat."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you, Robo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine Robo-san had salmon\Nwith a spinach cream pasta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Note: Echoing "Essays in Idleness,"\N{\an7}a work by the Buddhist monk Kenko
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Idle grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,When asked what she ate last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,she responds not with what she ate,\Nbut with the title of the book she read!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How stately! You are so wonderful, Robo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We sat in the yard and idly ate grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?! Your family always does that\Njust before payday, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They live in that big house, but it's a mystery\Nwhether they're rich or poor, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Next, let's tell each other\Nwhat we want the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Note: A nod to Doraemon\NI want a 4th dimensional pocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Wota?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not an object.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What you want only exists in the world\Nwhere there's cat-shaped robots!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And Robo-san? Don't tell me she wants a boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, Robo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A bo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A body of samples for anti-aging\NDNA manipulation experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Robo, I think you're going to get\Narrested one of these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I would not make such a blunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born so that I could be a sample\Nfor one of her experiments!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, see ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chikuwa Bookstore
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I was fine with just looking,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but if I could actually get to speak with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If our eyes could meet as we engaged in talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How brightly this world would shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've run through this simulation so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have an ace up my sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is needed for a man and woman\Nwho don't know each other to get acquainted...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why is my Friend's House
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes: Points in common!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-where did you buy that book?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, for... For a while now I've thought,\N"That sure looks interesting!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've looked around for it\Nbut I haven't been able to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,These days you can just buy things online,\Nso maybe this was a bit of a stretch...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chikuwa Bookstore\Nat the station's north entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're that interested in it, I will give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-she's talking to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem the household of\Na friend of yours is faced with difficulty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She's really talking to me right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why is my Friend's House\N{\an8}Slightly Smelly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,True enough, Sasaki kept five hamsters at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and Aoyama's house, where you had to pass\Nthrough the veranda to get to the bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:10:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,both of these were slightly smelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I've found my own answer\Nto this philosophical dilemma,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I will try speaking to you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear... How bright the setting sun is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}GRAAARGH!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Bzzzt
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Robo. I said I'm sorry!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's get along
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This cannot be solved by a simple apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it may be hard for me to show it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,even I can get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now Saginomiya-san and Tanaka-san are fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,S..Saginomiya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,P-please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's sort of unusual for you two to be fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Saginomiya-san, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always so calm,\Nso for you to worked up like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Robo doesn't get angry that often.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She and I don't really get into fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. There may have been one time, long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,J-just tell me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand that look you've got on your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, you can confide in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If that will make you feel even a little better, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, Robo, Wota, and I\Nwent to the same elementary school...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play Cops and Robbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the cop, and Kikuchi and Saginomiya\Nwill be the robbers, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We always played together after school,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Come on! Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but Robo ended up going to\Na prep school in the next town over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She may not look it, but she's super smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, when Wota and I went to different classes,\Nwe just fell out of touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We all led our own lives in middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but we ran into each other\Nduring the summer of our third year,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and we started hanging out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,By that time, Wota and I had\Nalready decided to go to Saijo. Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go to Saijo too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But you could get into\Na much better school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I have made my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you thinking?!\NDon't throw your life away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not presume to decide my life for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the first time I'd seen Robo get emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard later that she was\Npretty much alone at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, people couldn't tell what she was thinking,\Nso they just avoided her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to figure out why she chose Saijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, Wota stopped talking to me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We all went our separate ways again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,S-so that's what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I was so happy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,when the three of us met again in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}1st-year Class Lists
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same class?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, we're in the same grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well of course that's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my! What a wonderful story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what caused the fight this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,After school yesterday, I kinda killed Robo's pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's way too flippant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah, I kinda messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be surprised if she hates you for life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But, you get where I'm going, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When I say "pet," it's the\Nmicroorganisms that Robo cultivates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Microorganisms?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Robo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That new comic "Shakure-zamurai"\Nis super entertaining, so you should read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}New serial\N{\an8}Shakure-zamurai
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I accidentally smashed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I kinda feel like I've wasted my time listening to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Robo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You came back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shakure-zamurai was quite entertaining,\Nso I will forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it?! I'm looking forward to the next installment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If it had been me, would I have been able to say\Nshe shouldn't throw her life away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ashamed of myself for simply being happy\Nat the grade-level advancement list...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no end of worry for a girl in love, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What I have for Saginomiya-san is respect,\Nwhich isn't the same as romantic feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to try to make it\Nblack and white, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A person's feelings are vague\Nand can fall into, like, gray areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem like you have some experience with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I do have experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard a lot of your personal concerns...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're okay not swearing me to secrecy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I might accidentally tell someone, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you'd say anything, Someya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's what I want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A classmate I can share my concerns with...\NSomeya-san, you may be the first one for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what people refer to as "best friends"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This! THIS is why you bug me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?! You've got too much potential for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this because I went said we might be best friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for any bother-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There! That face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You really stir up feminine instincts, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact you do it without realizing makes it even\Nmore wicked! Five years in prison for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,See? There's that expression again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to have you come all the way out here with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, Takahashi. Do you best out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you at school tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I will definitely get closer to Robo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And if things go well, to us being in a relationship...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I will watch from here and witness your brave stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I'm your best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, that convenience store employee-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Robo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,D-do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You lent me this book a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, if it will not take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,W-well then, we'll just be going now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What for?! Let's hear what he has to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Read between the lines, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I wanna break this apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna let you get the jump on us, Robo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Get all complicated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I-I'm sorry. It looks like you were out with your friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,May all your front teeth suddenly fall out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,May you bite the inside of your cheek
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I don't mind. So, what did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and it gets all throbby!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Your left and your right cheeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Um... Th-that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Me... Me and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't. When push comes to shove,\NI don't have the courage to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"Me and"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah. Me and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and this guy, his name is Aoyama.\NWe really get along, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been my friend since middle school,\Nand he's a really good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But, the thing is, his house is slightly smelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Huh? Wait, me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:17:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering why, and when I thought about it,\NI came up with about 10 reasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what the hell am I talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She couldn't possibly be interested in listening to this-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you tell me about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it. She's interested in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, his house faces north,\Nand it's got bad ventilation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, there's damp, half-dried laundry\Nconstantly in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The garbage in the kitchen is in\Na constant state of neglect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the shoe cabinet at the front door\Nis stuffed with old, worn-out shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that more than meets the necessary definition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! The thing is, I thought about why people\Nperceive odors like that as being "smelly."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the perception of danger, born from instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! It's an intrinsic function,\Nfor the purpose of avoiding dangerous things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,When I think of that, I'm left with one hypothesis:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell from Aoyama's house might mean that\NI'm rejecting Aoyama on a genetic level!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm being genetically rejected?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This could also be the case when seen\Nfrom a philosophical viewpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the smell at Aoyama's house\Neven actually exist? In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoyama's house may not even actually be smelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:18:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be that the aversion I feel toward Aoyama\Nis just making me perceive it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He straight-up said "aversion"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is that aversion?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoyama has a childhood friend, a girl,\Nand they really get along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There might've been a part of me that was jealous,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,because he could go in and out of\Na girl's room like it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I see now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The book you gave me helped me to identify\Nthe negative feelings I've had.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Today was about me\Nwanting to show you my gratitude, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Why do we have to\Ntake the time to be considerate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, if she gets a boyfriend,\Nhe might introduce us to his guy friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You are smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can get this jealous,\Nyou must like your friend very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoyama is my number one best friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Robo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}H-hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to cheer you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you a lot too, Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Takahashi! Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll lend this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an odor meter, "Smell Sensor-kun."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it to measure a wet dog's odor index,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but it seems like the situation between you two\Nis more dire, so please use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You can return it after the facts regarding\Nyour friend's house have been clarified.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Robo! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Never mind our almost smothering friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the odor meter, and the slight awkwardness, she left...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the plan to have him\Nintroduce us to some guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, did you actually like that Takahashi dude?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If such represents the elation of having found\Na candidate for the purpose of
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,anti-aging DNA manipulation, then yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yasaka Station
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Teishotoku P has uploaded a new song!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that Vocalo P you've been\Nnuts about from before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still pretty unknown,\Nbut he must be an awesome guy. I like-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To say that you "like" him,\Nwhen you haven't even met him is just, "Ewe!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:20:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You can get a feel\Njust by listening to his songs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you met him in person, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd say that I like him, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Eew!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The afternoon song shines, in the corner of the room
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Secret•Sequence\N{\an7}Teishotoku P here. This is my fifth release.\N{\an7}I made this when I was gazing at sushi that just passed me by...\N{\an7}Teishotoku-P-san\N{\an8}Views\N{\an8}# of comments\N{\an9}# in my list
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My numbers aren't going up...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}All I do is wait, hoping for the revolution to begin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a time I thought\Nthat if I became a famous producer,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be able to go out with college women.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I have to hurry and come up with an answer
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm here today again\N{\an8}You do make nice songs\N{\an8}This song really permeates
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way such a sweet deal could be real!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Though I don't know the reason why I should hurry
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, I'm surrounded by high school girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But, no way! I'm glad I don't have one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm free! I don't have to spend money on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Regrets, I repeat them and cry
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I don't have a girlfriend! It's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But I mourn the fact that I can't change
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Soft\N{\an8}It's nice\N{\an8}I want the album\N{\an9}It's lovely
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I should get some sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The same class? Together? Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Second-year Class Assignments\N{\an8}(If you wish to change courses, please notify staff ASAP)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Shiori Saginomiya\N{\an7}Liberal\N{\an7}Arts\N{\an8}Akane Kikuchi\N{\an8}Nozomu Tanaka\NPending
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawagashikute yakamashikute
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Demo itoshikute
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ano hi no warai koe
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki modesenai story
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Seishun te yatsu wa zutto hikari to kage
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurayami no naka
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagayaku rettousei
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Furi kaereba kojiraseta
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Utsukushi sugiru hibi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Itsumo haru wa fui ni toori sugita ato
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi no kotoba mune ni reverb
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Itsuka haru ga zenbu tsure satte shimau
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sono hi made wa baka de ii
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kake nukeru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.35,0:22:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamamoto, you know I said I'd be\Ncollecting notebooks after the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.81,0:22:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The only ones who haven't turned them in\Nare you and Tanaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.27,0:22:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can look away all you want,\Nbut that won't make it go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! Last night was the night before the test!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.62,0:22:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, together, come on, say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to my usual noodle shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And what I ate there was tsukemen, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.46,0:22:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The store owner's like, "How's today's noodles?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Took only a sec to fire back with:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.55,0:22:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Barikata."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.93,0:22:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's "firm" to you, y'all. Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.27,0:22:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you this time, Yamamoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Note: MEN means "Noodles"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Men men me-me-men! Men me-men!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.56,0:23:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamamoto. I am asking about your notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot my backpack at the ramen shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.41,0:23:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've caused a lot of trouble for my parents. Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.20,0:23:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, it was in your bag,\Nwhich you left behind at the ramen yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you just say so?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, if you sang that chorus again,\NI would have used a pressure point to immobilize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.21,0:23:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Please, just let me just say this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.31,0:23:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, for real!
